The first smart bus powered by 5G technology  is seen in Zhengzhou, Central China's Henan Province, on Tuesday. Passengers can connect their smartphones to Wi-Fi under the 5G network. An 8G movie can be downloaded within a dozen seconds on the bus. Photo: IC Newspaper headline: Smart ride 
